## ğŸ§© Examples of Public-Domain vs. Protected Expression

| Example | Public-Domain Element | Protected Expression |
|----------|----------------------|----------------------|
| Superhero stories | â€œA person gains powers and fights evil.â€ | Specific hero designs, names, origin stories. |
